title: ICE with `associated_const_equality`

labels.name: I-ICE
labels.description: Issue: The compiler panicked, giving an Internal Compilation Error (ICE) ❄️

labels.name: T-compiler
labels.description: Relevant to the compiler team, which will review and decide on the PR/issue.

body:
Trying to remove `struct Const` workaround I get this ICE. https://github.com/stm32-rs/stm32f4xx-hal/commit/2f50fd5962db9bf3303c184744b274d080eb5916 Related to #92827 Note.
